  >
    <p class="label">Open Source</p>
    <h2 class="heading--sm" style="margin-top:0.75rem">
      Built in public.<br /><span class="grad"
        >By developers, for developers.</span
      >
    </h2>
    <p class="subheading" style="margin-top:1rem;text-align:center">
      Ignite is Apache 2.0 licensed. The entire codebase is Rust + TypeScript.
